    "description": {
      "value": "<em>By using lay on hands, you can bring the dead back to life.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Cha 19, Greater Mercy, lay on hands, mercy class feature.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>You can expend 10 uses of lay on hands to bring a single dead creature you touch back to life as a raise dead spell with a caster level equal to your paladin level. You must provide the material component for raise dead or choose to accept 1 temporary negative level; this level automatically goes away after 24 hours, never becomes a permanent negative level, and cannot be overcome in any way except by waiting for the duration to expire. ",
